(163, 3, 'Students in urban areas receive excellent STEM instruction while rural students have no access to education at all.'),
(163, 4, 'The region has the world''s youngest population with great potential, yet it lacks the institutional infrastructure to develop that talent.'),
(164, 1, 'They leverage existing affordable technology rather than requiring expensive new infrastructure, making them accessible even in remote areas.'),
